title: cyber security skills
extract: So, it is essential for cybersecurity experts to equip their cybersecurity arsenal with all the new up and coming technologies. Build a well-rounded skill set with skills ranging from penetration testing, IOT security, network security, identity, and access management, to other cyber-governance related soft-skills.Oct 8, 2018
